Package io.confluent.ksql.api.client

Class KsqlObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.ksql.api.client.KsqlObject
  • public class KsqlObject
extends Object
    A representation of a map of string keys to values. Useful for representing a JSON object.
